[1]      [ 0       0      1]  [1]

translation and rotation

[ x' ]   [ cos a   -sin a   h]   [x]
[y'  ] = [ sin a   cos a    k] . [y]
[1]    = [  0       0       1]   [1]

this is a multiply
x' = cos a * x - sin a * y + h
y' = sin a * x + cos a * y +k